@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "FAQ";
}

<body>
    <div class="container py-5">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-8">
                <h1 class="main-heading">FAQ</h1>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4">
                <p class="side-text">
                    Smartphones, tablets, laptops,<br>
                    and components with delivery<br>
                    across Singapore.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content-section">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <h2 class="section-heading">
                        What types of devices do you sell?
                    </h2>
                    <div class="section-divider"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-8 offset-lg-4">
                    <p class="description-text">
                        1. We specialize in premium smartphones from Apple, Samsung, Google, and OnePlus, along with tablets from iPad to Surface Pro. Our laptop selection includes MacBooks, ThinkPads, and gaming rigs from ASUS and MSI. We also stock components like SSDs, RAM, processors, and graphics cards for custom builds.                   </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content-section">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <h2 class="section-heading">
                        How fast is your delivery across Singapore?
                    </h2>
                    <div class="section-divider"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-8 offset-lg-4">
                    <p class="description-text">
                        2. Same-day delivery is available for orders placed before 2 PM within central Singapore. Standard delivery takes 1-2 business days island-wide. We offer free shipping on orders above $150, with express delivery options available for urgent purchases at competitive rates.                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content-section">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <h2 class="section-heading">
                        Do you provide warranty and after-sales support?
                    </h2>
                    <div class="section-divider"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-8 offset-lg-4">
                    <p class="description-text">
                        3. All devices come with manufacturer warranties ranging from 1-3 years depending on the product. We provide local warranty service through our authorized repair center, plus 30-day return policy for unopened items. Our technical support team offers free consultation for setup and troubleshooting.                   </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content-section">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <h2 class="section-heading">
                        Can I trade in my old device for a new one?
                    </h2>
                    <div class="section-divider"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-8 offset-lg-4">
                    <p class="description-text">
                        4. Yes! We accept trade-ins for smartphones, tablets, and laptops in working condition. Our assessment team provides instant quotes based on device model, age, and condition. Trade-in credits can be applied directly to your new purchase, making upgrades more affordable.                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content-section">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <h2 class="section-heading">
                        Do you offer installation and setup services?
                    </h2>
                    <div class="section-divider"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-8 offset-lg-4">
                    <p class="description-text">
                        5. Our certified technicians provide complete setup services including data transfer, software installation, and device configuration. We also offer component installation for custom PC builds, smart home device setup, and network configuration. Service fees vary by complexity.                   </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content-section">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <h2 class="section-heading">
                        What payment methods do you accept?
                    </h2>
                    <div class="section-divider"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-8 offset-lg-4">
                    <p class="description-text">
                        6. We accept all major credit cards, PayNow, GrabPay, and bank transfers. Installment plans are available through our partners for purchases above $500. Corporate accounts can arrange NET 30 payment terms with proper documentation and credit approval.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content-section">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <h2 class="section-heading">
                        How can I track my order and stay updated?
                    </h2>
                    <div class="section-divider"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-8 offset-lg-4">
                    <p class="description-text">
                        7. Once your order is confirmed, you'll receive SMS and email notifications with tracking details. Our customer portal allows real-time order tracking, delivery scheduling, and communication with our logistics team. Push notifications keep you informed at every step of the process.                  </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
    </div>
</body>